					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The DPCM channel can only represent silence by railing (i.e. going to 0 or 126) or stopping. Otherwise, the quietest idle value is -36dBFS.<br /><br />Correspondingly, you could either manually edit the source file to go to + or - full scale during silences during the recording (with the understanding that this may add an audible click); you could slice up the file into multiple segments; or you could intentionally add a sound that would be acceptable in the background instead.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

